{"tid":2368843,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普《Home Alone》鏡頭恐被刪 男主角舉腳贊成","createTime":"2021-01-16T14:16:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-19T07:27:37.000Z","uid":202966,"like":2,"dislike":51,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"83c26fa05f6f2dcaf6a5e799048d3857adb05e0a","tid":2368843,"uid":202966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T14:16:01.000Z","msg":"美國現任總統特朗普被指煽動示威者，闖入國會山莊引發國會暴亂。特朗普亦被多個社交媒體封殺的同時，亦可能被刪走在《寶貝智多星2之玩轉紐約》（Home Alone 2: Lost in New York）的客串鏡頭。有網民發起聯署，要求刪走特朗普在《Home Alone 2》的身影，就連《Home Alone 2》的男主角都表示贊成。<br />\n<br />\n這套電影每年聖誕都有不少人重溫。除了網民發起聯署刪走特朗普鏡頭外，亦有網民坐言起行，動手刪走特朗普鏡頭，並把片段上載至社交平台Twitter。<br />\n<br />\n此已刪減的片段，就連電影男主角麥哥利高堅（Macaulay Culkin）都看到，麥哥利高堅更在Twitter留言「做得好（Bravo）」。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，加拿大廣播公司（CBC）較早前重播《寶貝智多星2之玩轉紐約》時，亦已刪走特朗普鏡頭。CBC當時解釋指，刪走電影中八分鐘的片段，是因為要播廣告。他強調，有關剪輯早在特朗普當選美國總統之前已完成，又澄清此舉並非出於政治動機。<br />\n<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-B3YBdmHiQTY/XgU59Sg22XI/AAAAAAAEb3E/XBGMCVPumJkpXgYCRJXHLioJ95N3-T3vwCLcBGAsYHQ/s1600/AlarmingPlainHarpyeagle-size_restricted.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-B3YBdmHiQTY%2FXgU59Sg22XI%2FAAAAAAAEb3E%2FXBGMCVPumJkpXgYCRJXHLioJ95N3-T3vwCLcBGAsYHQ%2Fs1600%2FAlarmingPlainHarpyeagle-size_restricted.gif&h=060a4fdc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b30d04cb5c0b6fa1c3a43b021b4dbd87cf221213","tid":2368843,"uid":280648,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T14:17:59.000Z","msg":"原來佢有上鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d2637a946b9880103e7215ddfd03a458e4f0cca","tid":2368843,"uid":226955,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T14:18:03.000Z","msg":"呢條男主角好似吸開毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f1fd319d1648b9e9621023aff8171f1445cb13c","tid":2368843,"uid":80093,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T14:20:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=